00:07.991 --> 00:09.625
We've tried everything.

00:09.627 --> 00:11.176
We're covered
in Drakkar,

00:11.178 --> 00:12.494
I've got fresh
new white socks,

00:12.496 --> 00:14.179
and I thought our
mime work in there

00:14.181 --> 00:16.215
was excellent!

00:16.216 --> 00:17.382
What?

00:22.806 --> 00:26.725
